pull.title: Remove progress bar on modal overlay
pull.body:
This PR removes the progress bar (keeping only the percentage) on modal overlay 

resolves #279

events.message: Remove progress bar on modal overlay

events.body: tACK https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gui/pull/300/commits/61fd8fe9a1ddb866ad0a41d053003e78c395f739 on Windows 10. Unnecessary Progress bar no longer there :)

Concept ACK.

@brunoerg 

For such PRs it is convenient to have screenshots "before/master" and "after/PR" posted in the PR description.

UPDATE. Also you can use on of these [words](https://docs.github.com/en/github/managing-your-work-on-github/linking-a-pull-request-to-an-issue#linking-a-pull-request-to-an-issue-using-a-keyword) instead of "See" to link to the issue :)
